This is a faithful TrueType reproduction of the IBM PC VGA 8x16 text-mode
ROM font: a fixed-pitch (monospace) bitmap face. It is used by the grid
typography renderer (receipt_grid.py) to draw synthetic thermal receipts as
a fixed character grid with hard (non-anti-aliased) dots, matching the look
of dot-matrix / thermal receipt printers.

